title: 203 - The Island Boys Stole Our Money?
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a full hause of characters. The boys waste no time todays episode jumping right into the POD Fod, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s FOD was a plethora of new and upcoming movies, including but not limited too Training Day prequel, new Batman, a full list of upcoming movies to save theaters, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
